# Environment Configuration

## Required Variables
IDP_URL=https://idp.xaaplayground.dev
AUTH_SERVER_URL=https://auth.resource.xaaplayground.dev
TODO_RESOURCE_SERVER=https://api.resource.xaaplayground.dev
CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret
RESOURCE_CLIENT_ID=your-resource-client-id
RESOURCE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-resource-client-secret

## Security - CRITICAL: Must be set to a random secret in production
SESSION_SECRET=CHANGE_THIS_TO_A_SECURE_RANDOM_STRING_IN_PRODUCTION

## Optional
NODE_ENV=development


